# Git Commit Coauthor

When creating git commits, add a coauthor line at the end of the commit message.

## Format

```
<commit message>

coauthor: Cursor
```

## Example

```bash
git commit -m "$(cat <<'EOF'
Add validation for user input

coauthor: Cursor
EOF
)"
```
